      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].lines.Array.size
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.size
      value: 11
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[0].text
      value: Well, now about your mission. Are you ready?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[1].text
      value: Ay ay, captain?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[2].text
      value: 'Bring me the trident of Nuptun '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[3].text
      value: ...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[4].text
      value: Whaaaaat?!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[5].text
      value: How am I going to do this!?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[6].text
      value: Well, with the new spell, you can breathe underwater, so it's a lot
        easier.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[7].text
      value: 'That''s not what I''m talking about! How do I take the trident from
        Neptune?! '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[8].text
      value: Yes, whatever. Or have you changed your mind about learning magic?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[9].text
      value: ... No I haven't ...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[10].text
      value: That's it, just come with a trident.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[11].text
      value: All right, then follow me to my tower.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2406992749507461194, guid: 9ebdd227594542a4497eea67b7cdd6f7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogLines.Array.data[0].dialogueLines.Array.data[12].text
      value: All right, then follow me to my tower.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
